<i>adjective</i>: 철석같다 [철썩깓따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>철석같다 [철썩깓따]</dt><br>
<dd>firm; resolute; adamant</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 의지, 약속 등이 쇠와 돌처럼 매우 굳고 단단하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind, will, word, etc., being very firm and steadfast just like iron and stone.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>